data.description:
OPEN HOUSE 11/12 2-4pm
Nestled off one of Flat Rock road's most peaceful neighborhoods, this stunning 5 bedroom, 2.5 bath home is a true oasis. Step inside the light-filled living room and you're greeted by an open and airy floor plan ideal for entertaining. The kitchen features ample counter space, lots of cabinetry, and high-end stainless appliances. It flows seamlessly into the expansive family room bathed in natural light with a cozy fireplace - the perfect spot to relax after a long day. Escape to the lavish primary bedroom suite - this spa-like retreat, a luxurious bath with dual vanities, an oversized walk-in shower, and not just one but two huge walk-in closets. You'll enjoy peaceful nights' sleep in this sumptuous sanctuary. Upstairs find 4 additional bedrooms each with their own spacious closets and plenty of room for family or guests. The second-floor laundry room adds convenience. Outside, the private fenced backyard and gazebo provide the perfect spot to enjoy the outdoors. Just a few steps away you are greeted by the beauty of Long Run Park.  Join the Polo Fields Golf and Social Club for additional amenities. Showings are filling up fast for this move-in ready home that has been meticulously maintained. Just minutes from fabulous shopping and dining, this is an incredible opportunity to live in Flat Rock Ridge, a most desirable neighborhood. Call today to schedule your private tour!
